1
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:33,330
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,350 --> 00:00:36,320
[Episode 18]

3
00:00:37,070 --> 00:00:37,880
My Lady.

4
00:00:38,790 --> 00:00:42,110
Now I can no longer help you
restore spiritual power.

5
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:45,750
Or...

6
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:52,620
do you want to spend more time with me?

7
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:04,120
Bai Shanjun.

8
00:01:04,870 --> 00:01:09,120
In the past, you were
always so formal and respectful.

9
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:13,510
But now...

10
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:18,230
you've grown bolder.

11
00:01:20,710 --> 00:01:23,560
I am merely treating you
the way you treated me.

12
00:01:24,510 --> 00:01:25,310
My Lady,

13
00:01:25,710 --> 00:01:28,560
a dying man speaks without restraint.

14
00:01:29,510 --> 00:01:32,070
Please bear with me.

15
00:01:37,830 --> 00:01:38,750
Don't worry.

16
00:01:39,380 --> 00:01:40,910
I'll figure something out.

17
00:01:41,590 --> 00:01:44,000
Okay, I trust you.

18
00:01:47,039 --> 00:01:48,039
It's late.

19
00:01:48,430 --> 00:01:50,789
The mountain road is treacherous.
Be careful.

20
00:01:50,789 --> 00:01:51,990
Don't worry, My Lady.

21
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,560
Xiaohu is very smart.

22
00:01:53,789 --> 00:01:56,590
He's already outside
with a carriage ready for me.

23
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:58,640
My Lady,

24
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:01,040
I won't take my health lightly.

25
00:02:58,290 --> 00:02:59,079
My Lady.

26
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:03,850
My Lady.

27
00:03:07,510 --> 00:03:08,760
I see you.

28
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:11,230
Are you reluctant

29
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:13,710
to die just like this?

30
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,560
I'm... not reluctant.

31
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:22,840
In the past,

32
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,960
I had a clear conscience.

33
00:03:25,420 --> 00:03:26,820
I don't regret anything.

34
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:30,500
Meeting you at Yin-Yang Crossing

35
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:32,670
is the happiest thing in my life.

36
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:34,579
You are the best person

37
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:36,340
I have ever met.

38
00:04:00,190 --> 00:04:01,150
I am a demon,

39
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,080
not a person.

40
00:04:05,670 --> 00:04:07,110
Whether human or demon,

41
00:04:08,140 --> 00:04:09,580
you are like a deity.

42
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,580
I dare not profane you.

43
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:16,920
It's just...

44
00:04:18,310 --> 00:04:19,279
I'm thinking,

45
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,160
if...

46
00:04:22,910 --> 00:04:23,880
I die,

47
00:04:25,270 --> 00:04:26,070
My Lady,

48
00:04:28,270 --> 00:04:29,630
you must remember me.

49
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:51,360
Your words are very pleasant to hear,

50
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,580
but you shouldn't have...

51
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:58,240
played tricks right under my nose.

52
00:05:05,290 --> 00:05:05,960
My Lady.

53
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,600
I...

54
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:14,430
I heard about what happened from Shuan,

55
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,630
so I thought

56
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:18,680
that if he could enter my dream,

57
00:05:18,750 --> 00:05:20,800
I might get some new clues.

58
00:05:22,590 --> 00:05:23,920
Then why hide it from me?

59
00:05:26,430 --> 00:05:27,720
It was risky after all.

60
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,800
I was worried you wouldn't allow it.

61
00:05:32,630 --> 00:05:33,630
You taking risks—

62
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,600
what does that have to do with me?

63
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:41,510
I just wanted

64
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:44,040
to do a little more

65
00:05:46,610 --> 00:05:47,810
wherever I still can.

66
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:55,060
It's useless.

67
00:05:56,270 --> 00:05:59,130
You have no selfish thoughts or greed
in your heart.

68
00:05:59,790 --> 00:06:01,710
The evil power can't touch you.

69
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:03,680
Besides,

70
00:06:04,270 --> 00:06:05,480
with me by your side,

71
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:07,450
he wouldn't dare show himself.

72
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:10,950
I hadn't thought of that.

73
00:06:17,870 --> 00:06:19,310
What you just said...

74
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:21,830
was sleep talk?

75
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,040
Of course.

76
00:06:27,540 --> 00:06:29,600
In my dream, I was not in my right mind,

77
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:32,159
so I spoke out of turn.

78
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,070
I know

79
00:06:37,570 --> 00:06:38,520
to you, I am

80
00:06:39,490 --> 00:06:43,020
but a fleeting moment in the vast sea—
born at dawn, gone by dusk.

81
00:06:43,980 --> 00:06:45,440
I am well aware of my place.

82
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:47,770
What you are to me

83
00:06:49,070 --> 00:06:50,720
is not for you to judge.

84
00:07:02,430 --> 00:07:03,040
My Lord,

85
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,510
are you asleep?

86
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:06,430
I...

87
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:07,990
Something's wrong.

88
00:07:07,990 --> 00:07:09,340
Sh-Shuan is missing.

89
00:07:09,370 --> 00:07:10,830
There's no one in the room.

90
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:19,680
Quiet, everyone!

91
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,570
Calm down, everyone!

92
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:21,740
[County Yamen]

93
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:21,720
Calm down!

94
00:07:22,470 --> 00:07:23,360
Don't push! Don't push!

95
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:25,630
My father must have been taken
by that demon!

96
00:07:25,630 --> 00:07:26,830
My Lord,

97
00:07:26,830 --> 00:07:28,750
you must save us!

98
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:31,430
My father handed in
the Fortune-Turning Stone

99
00:07:31,430 --> 00:07:33,159
because he listened to you!

100
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,390
Now he's been taken away.

101
00:07:34,390 --> 00:07:36,270
You have to save my father!

102
00:07:36,520 --> 00:07:37,390
Everyone, stop pushing!

103
00:07:37,390 --> 00:07:39,390
Calm down, everyone! Stop pushing!

104
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:41,159
Give me back my Fortune-Turning Stone!

105
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:42,680
We all handed them in

106
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,190
because we listened to you!

107
00:07:44,190 --> 00:07:45,159
His Lordship has his own arrangements!

108
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:45,920
Don't push!

109
00:07:46,590 --> 00:07:47,250
Don't push!

110
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,190
This is serious.

111
00:07:49,190 --> 00:07:50,510
Those who handed over gold yesterday

112
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:51,909
all vanished overnight.

113
00:07:51,940 --> 00:07:52,750
It's the same on my side.

114
00:07:52,750 --> 00:07:53,830
Over 10 people on the official register

115
00:07:53,830 --> 00:07:57,090
have all vanished—
no one seen alive, no bodies recovered.

116
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:03,000
Could it be that the evil spirit
really has manifested

117
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,400
and punished those who broke the contract?

118
00:08:05,420 --> 00:08:06,550
What he wants more is

119
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,690
to control people with fear

120
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:10,140
and create more chaos,

121
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,310
so that everyone

122
00:08:11,310 --> 00:08:13,240
will never dare to defy his will again.

123
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,480
But if he truly had such power,

124
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:16,040
why did he
go through all that trouble before,

125
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,360
using gold to lure mortals

126
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:19,600
into killing and spreading rumors for him?

127
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,360
It seems

128
00:08:21,180 --> 00:08:21,940
this time,

129
00:08:22,070 --> 00:08:25,130
he has gained a helper
who knows Yin-Yang Crossing well

130
00:08:25,310 --> 00:08:27,480
and can assist him.

131
00:08:28,630 --> 00:08:29,510
Darn it.

132
00:08:30,510 --> 00:08:32,750
Shuan is... is so young.

133
00:08:33,630 --> 00:08:35,690
I hope nothing really happens to him.

134
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:40,080
Never tell a third person.

135
00:08:40,870 --> 00:08:42,909
Never leave this stone.

136
00:08:43,309 --> 00:08:45,550
Never regret this deal.

137
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:50,360
Violate it, and the bond breaks. Your soul
will be scattered to the Three Paths.

138
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:53,010
Have you forgotten our agreement?

139
00:09:00,510 --> 00:09:01,320
You,

140
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:03,630
come here.

141
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,850
You are terrified, aren't you?

142
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:44,630
Don't be afraid. I'll take you home.

143
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:59,950
Whispers echo in the forest,
each cry like weeping.

144
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:06,670
Mimicking human speech,
it drains away vitality.

145
00:10:08,510 --> 00:10:13,120
Old things return,
shifting within the heart.

146
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:22,080
Not their rightful owner—
calamity will not cease.

147
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:32,100
I underestimated the enemy too much.

148
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:34,850
When it comes to underestimating him,

149
00:10:34,850 --> 00:10:35,850
I am also to blame.

150
00:10:37,090 --> 00:10:38,690
I've known him for 100 years.

151
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,460
I know his methods very well—

152
00:10:40,460 --> 00:10:42,120
brute force and bewitchment.

153
00:10:42,750 --> 00:10:46,500
This time, he's exploited people's hearts
to build a network

154
00:10:47,220 --> 00:10:49,080
and even learned to manage a lair.

155
00:10:49,850 --> 00:10:52,250
These are new tactics I never anticipated.

156
00:10:53,070 --> 00:10:54,630
Master, Lord Bai.

157
00:10:55,030 --> 00:10:55,840
Master,

158
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:57,150
I have found out.

159
00:10:57,150 --> 00:10:58,670
The story of the Fortune-Turning Master

160
00:10:58,670 --> 00:11:00,800
first appeared about half a month ago.

161
00:11:01,030 --> 00:11:02,910
Qian Wanqian,
the owner of the Wanqian Bank,

162
00:11:02,910 --> 00:11:04,550
told it at a banquet.

163
00:11:04,550 --> 00:11:06,000
He spoke with absolute certainty,

164
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:07,320
claiming that he made his fortune

165
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,150
originally because of the help

166
00:11:08,150 --> 00:11:10,080
from the Fortune-Turning Master.

167
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:12,120
The bank's owner?

168
00:11:13,550 --> 00:11:16,440
He's always had a good reputation
at Yin-Yang Crossing.

169
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,170
He's trustworthy in business.

170
00:11:18,490 --> 00:11:21,040
In times of famine,
he often gave out porridge and rice.

171
00:11:21,040 --> 00:11:23,370
By the way, Master, you've met him before.

172
00:11:26,470 --> 00:11:27,430
I remember him.

173
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:30,120
About half a year ago,

174
00:11:30,750 --> 00:11:33,880
he knelt outside Xiqianhua Mansion
for an entire night.

175
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:35,360
Lady Fufeng!

176
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,720
Lady Fufeng!

177
00:11:38,630 --> 00:11:39,790
Lady Fufeng!

178
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:41,190
Lady Fufeng!

179
00:11:41,330 --> 00:11:43,690
Please show your face, Lady Fufeng!

180
00:11:43,910 --> 00:11:45,840
For my sake,

181
00:11:45,860 --> 00:11:48,620
please save my son, Lady Fufeng!

182
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:52,960
Your son's illness
has already reached his heart meridians.

183
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:55,020
There is nothing Her Ladyship can do.

184
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,360
Please go back.

185
00:11:56,380 --> 00:11:59,350
But... But Lady Fufeng is a demon!

186
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:02,240
She is a great demon! A deity!

187
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:05,720
Lady Fufeng.

188
00:12:06,670 --> 00:12:08,960
If... If you can save my son,

189
00:12:09,510 --> 00:12:12,150
I... I will give all my wealth!

190
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:16,040
I... I'm willing to trade my life for his!

191
00:12:16,070 --> 00:12:17,120
Lady Fufeng!

192
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:25,510
Human illness is a human tribulation.

193
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:29,150
Demonic power can't cure human diseases.

194
00:12:29,790 --> 00:12:31,720
If his fate has brought him to this,

195
00:12:32,940 --> 00:12:34,230
even I can do nothing.

196
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:38,270
Lady Fufeng!

197
00:12:38,550 --> 00:12:39,480
Lady Fufeng!

198
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,360
Lady Fufeng!

199
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:44,080
I beg you, Lady Fufeng!

200
00:12:44,350 --> 00:12:46,060
Please save my son!

201
00:12:46,090 --> 00:12:47,550
-Lady Fufeng!
-Please go back.

202
00:12:47,550 --> 00:12:50,080
Lady Fufeng, I beg you!

203
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:52,130
Lady Fufeng,

204
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:54,870
save my son!

205
00:12:54,890 --> 00:12:57,200
Lady Fufeng, save him!

206
00:12:58,690 --> 00:13:00,330
Save him.

207
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:01,790
Lady Fufeng.

208
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,910
Save him,

209
00:13:03,910 --> 00:13:05,320
Lady Fufeng!

210
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:11,480
Lady Fufeng.

211
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,330
What happened then?

212
00:13:16,630 --> 00:13:18,840
Then, within two months,

213
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:20,720
the Qian family held a funeral.

214
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:22,520
It caused quite a stir back then.

215
00:13:22,790 --> 00:13:24,720
Qian Wanqian was listless all day long.

216
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:27,000
And the bank was closed for quite a while.

217
00:13:28,770 --> 00:13:31,840
If we connect all these events together,

218
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,820
they do seem a bit unusual.

219
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:36,060
Qian Wanqian knelt and begged
but got nothing.

220
00:13:36,060 --> 00:13:38,860
In the end,
he still couldn't save his beloved son.

221
00:13:39,930 --> 00:13:41,790
But whether he hates Lady Fufeng,

222
00:13:42,100 --> 00:13:43,030
it's hard to say.

223
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:46,270
But what is certain is

224
00:13:46,790 --> 00:13:49,910
that afterward, he turned to the one
who could save him,

225
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:52,550
bless him, and change his fortune:

226
00:13:52,660 --> 00:13:53,360
Bai Han.

227
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:57,480
Qian Wanqian has the ability and channels

228
00:13:57,790 --> 00:13:59,630
to produce a large number of gold ingots

229
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:02,230
that have never appeared
on the market before.

230
00:14:02,270 --> 00:14:03,600
From this perspective,

231
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:05,630
the first pawn in the fortune-turning game

232
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:06,840
is Qian Wanqian.

233
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:09,160
I'll head to the Wanqian Bank right now.

234
00:14:09,240 --> 00:14:10,320
Without any evidence,

235
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:12,790
you'll only alert the enemy if you go now.

236
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:14,500
You are too impatient.

237
00:14:16,270 --> 00:14:18,670
Indeed, I am a bit hasty.

238
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:24,150
But is there any other way right now?

239
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:29,150
Since we can't get answers from people,

240
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,790
let the objects that can't lie

241
00:14:32,270 --> 00:14:33,750
tell us the truth.

242
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:50,240
Vulgar things. All vulgar things.

243
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:55,720
They are thin in spiritual energy,
like rotten wood unfit for carving.

244
00:15:00,630 --> 00:15:02,510
I didn't notice this before.

245
00:15:03,130 --> 00:15:05,550
This is actually a good thing.

246
00:15:07,020 --> 00:15:10,020
What a pity. What a pity.

247
00:15:10,160 --> 00:15:12,920
Elder Cha, what should I do?

248
00:15:13,410 --> 00:15:16,120
You must... save it.

249
00:15:19,750 --> 00:15:21,910
Please be very careful.

250
00:15:22,670 --> 00:15:25,030
You don't trust me?

251
00:15:25,450 --> 00:15:26,970
Then why did you come to me?

252
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,530
What are you talking about?

253
00:15:28,710 --> 00:15:31,320
Then thanks for your help, Elder Cha.

254
00:15:32,510 --> 00:15:35,670
Don't worry, I know what to do.

255
00:16:00,780 --> 00:16:01,440
Look.

256
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,840
To get an item,

257
00:16:04,270 --> 00:16:06,390
you don't necessarily
have to steal or rob.

258
00:16:06,390 --> 00:16:08,870
See into the deepest desires
in people's hearts,

259
00:16:08,870 --> 00:16:11,790
and someone
will naturally offer it to you.

260
00:16:12,550 --> 00:16:13,750
Thank you, Elder Cha.

261
00:16:14,550 --> 00:16:16,910
I am just an appraiser.

262
00:16:17,390 --> 00:16:19,510
To be able to serve Lady Fufeng

263
00:16:19,510 --> 00:16:21,000
is my utmost honor.

264
00:16:22,910 --> 00:16:25,790
This old man looks extraordinary.

265
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:27,450
I wonder what his true form is.

266
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:31,740
Elder Cha is a teapot spirit
who has cultivated for 100 years.

267
00:16:31,740 --> 00:16:32,740
His lineage

268
00:16:33,270 --> 00:16:36,630
possesses an extraordinary sensitivity
to objects that carry

269
00:16:36,630 --> 00:16:38,720
the weight of time and human intent.

270
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:44,480
Lord Bai, you're new here.
There's something you don't know.

271
00:16:44,870 --> 00:16:46,240
At Yin-Yang Crossing,

272
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:49,030
wealthy families collect antiques,

273
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:52,960
mostly with the intention
of cultivating objects into spirits.

274
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:55,720
If they can get an object
to cultivate into human form,

275
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:58,480
they may take it as an adopted child

276
00:16:58,690 --> 00:17:01,400
to strengthen the family's foundation,

277
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:04,720
or hire it as a capable assistant.

278
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:05,880
For example,

279
00:17:06,310 --> 00:17:09,440
if an old abacus becomes a spirit,

280
00:17:09,560 --> 00:17:13,040
it would be a genius
in the banking business.

281
00:17:13,550 --> 00:17:16,550
If an ancient sword
cultivates into human form,

282
00:17:16,790 --> 00:17:19,720
it could become a family guard.

283
00:17:19,720 --> 00:17:22,680
Therefore, an appraiser

284
00:17:22,829 --> 00:17:27,079
judges not only the authenticity
and age of objects,

285
00:17:27,589 --> 00:17:32,290
but also their potential and temperament
for transforming into human form.

286
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:36,000
Since the matter here is finished,

287
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:38,270
I will take my leave.

288
00:17:50,700 --> 00:17:52,590
According to Fengling's investigation,

289
00:17:52,590 --> 00:17:55,720
Qian Wanqian has worn this for decades.

290
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:57,560
He has never taken it off.

291
00:17:58,680 --> 00:18:00,630
So has it become a spirit now?

292
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:10,790
Its spiritual nature has emerged,

293
00:18:10,790 --> 00:18:13,590
but it's heavily suppressed
by Qian Wanqian's vulgarity

294
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:16,090
and his eagerness for quick success.

295
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:19,310
However, this is precisely what I want.

296
00:18:20,030 --> 00:18:23,160
Since its spiritual nature has emerged,
it can perceive the past.

297
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:25,030
Without independent consciousness,

298
00:18:25,030 --> 00:18:27,000
it won't lie or be biased.

299
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:30,720
Now I'm using the water
of the spiritual spring to activate it.

300
00:18:30,720 --> 00:18:32,070
What it reflects

301
00:18:32,640 --> 00:18:35,680
are the memory fragments
closest to the truth.

302
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:41,240
Now let's hear

303
00:18:41,750 --> 00:18:43,960
what this witness who can't lie

304
00:18:44,640 --> 00:18:46,200
has to tell us.

305
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:53,240
Yu.

306
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:56,350
My son.

307
00:18:58,550 --> 00:19:00,550
I truly have no other way.

308
00:19:03,510 --> 00:19:05,030
I can't save you.

309
00:19:06,790 --> 00:19:09,510
Even Xiqianhua Mansion can't do anything.

310
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:13,720
Son,

311
00:19:15,030 --> 00:19:17,310
please don't blame me.

312
00:19:18,510 --> 00:19:19,550
Mortal,

313
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:22,240
you are crying.

314
00:19:23,510 --> 00:19:24,060
Who?

315
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:28,350
Who is talking there?

316
00:19:30,270 --> 00:19:32,680
It doesn't matter who I am.

317
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:34,350
What matters is

318
00:19:35,310 --> 00:19:40,310
if you want to save your Yu.

319
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:45,160
Can you really save Yu?

320
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:47,680
Can you really save him?

321
00:19:50,070 --> 00:19:51,030
I beg you.

322
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:54,400
If you can really save him,

323
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:56,030
I will do anything you ask.

324
00:19:56,620 --> 00:19:58,820
Even if it means spending all my wealth,

325
00:19:59,110 --> 00:20:00,550
I will not hesitate.

326
00:20:01,230 --> 00:20:02,200
Wealth

327
00:20:02,510 --> 00:20:03,840
is just a worldly thing.

328
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:05,630
What I need

329
00:20:05,650 --> 00:20:07,040
is your loyalty,

330
00:20:07,070 --> 00:20:08,160
your devotion,

331
00:20:08,550 --> 00:20:11,550
and every descendant of the Qian family

332
00:20:11,550 --> 00:20:13,110
to be used by me.

333
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:16,310
Okay. Okay.

334
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:19,000
As long as Yu can live.

335
00:20:19,580 --> 00:20:21,970
Then make a contract with me.

336
00:20:22,070 --> 00:20:24,000
I will grant your son a new life

337
00:20:24,020 --> 00:20:26,460
and guide you to endless wealth.

338
00:20:27,340 --> 00:20:30,010
And you, Qian Wanqian,

339
00:20:30,750 --> 00:20:33,400
shall become my agent in the mortal world,

340
00:20:33,720 --> 00:20:36,510
offer me loyalty of you
and your descendants,

341
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:37,720
and help me

342
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:40,750
restore order at Yin-Yang Crossing.

343
00:20:47,750 --> 00:20:50,640
Okay, I promise you,

344
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:53,090
as long as Yu can live.
